www.k-lite.tk seems to be down at the mo.. and the filename link is for people who have KaZaAlite with a program called sig2dat installed (its bundled with KaZaAlite). It just adds the file into your dowload queue, so you don't need to search. I find i have to cancel, and then resume the download, to get them to work using that though. Still easier than searching, and it's handy for verified files.
